### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### ============================================
### AUTH
### ============================================

### Register Admin User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### Register Operador User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "operador",
  "password": "operador123",
  "role": "OPERADOR"
}

### Login as Admin
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Login as Operador
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "operador",
  "password": "operador123"
}

### ============================================
### ROUTES (replace {{token}} with actual JWT)
### ============================================

### List Routes (paginated)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/routes?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List Routes with Filters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/routes?originCity=Bogotá&status=ACTIVA&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Route by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/routes/{{routeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Route (ADMIN only)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/routes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "originCity": "Bogotá",
  "destinationCity": "Medellín",
  "distanceKm": 415,
  "estimatedTimeHours": 8.5,
  "vehicleType": "CAMION",
  "carrier": "TCC",
  "costUsd": 320.00,
  "status": "ACTIVA"
}

### Update Route (ADMIN only)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/routes/{{routeId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "SUSPENDIDA",
  "costUsd": 350.00
}

### Soft Delete Route (ADMIN only)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/routes/{{routeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Import Routes from CSV (ADMIN only)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/routes/import
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="routes.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

id,origin_city,destination_city,distance_km,estimated_time_hours,vehicle_type,carrier,cost_usd,status,created_at
1,Bogotá,Medellín,415,8.5,CAMION,TCC,320.00,ACTIVA,2024-01-05T08:00:00Z
--boundary--

